<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/48026269-cathy-chan-pakyung"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1470977259i/48026269._UX100_CR0,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/48026269-cathy-chan-pakyung">Cathy Chan Pakyung</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">of course its partly because it was a gift from her best friend Chizuko, but i think it&apos;s more about the fact that Chizuko, who was never a superstiti<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">of course its partly because it was a gift from her best friend Chizuko, but i think it's more about the fact that Chizuko, who was never a superstitious person, came up with the idea and folded the crane for Sadako just to cheer her up. as we know Sadako believed in good luck charms. <br />so it's about how best friends do things just for each other.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
